e","categoryHTML":"<h2>Model zoo</h2><h3>TensorFlow Lite models</h3>","itemHTML":"<li>TensorFlow Lite models\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.tensorflow.org/lite/models\">TensorFlow Lite models</a> - With official Android and iOS examples.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.tensorflow.org/lite/guide/hosted_models\">Pretrained models</a> - Quantized and floating point variants.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://tfhub.dev/\">TensorFlow Hub</a> - Set \"Model format = TFLite\" to find TensorFlow Lite models.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-29T00:26:19.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"margaretmz/awesome-tensorflow-lite","categoryHTML":"<h2>Ideas and Inspiration</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ml-gde/e2e-tflite-tutorials\">E2E TFLite Tutorials</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ml-gde/e2e-tflite-tutorials\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">123</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":123,\"repo\":\"ml-gde/e2e-tflite-tutorials\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Checkout this repo for sample app ideas and seeking help for your tutorial projects. Once a project gets completed, the links of the TensorFlow Lite model(s), sample code and tutorial will be added to this awesome list.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-29T00:26:19.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"margaretmz/awesome-tensorflow-lite","categoryHTML":"<h2>Plugins and SDKs</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.edgeimpulse.com/\">Edge Impulse</a> - Created by <a href=\"https://twitter.com/EdgeImpulse\">@EdgeImpulse</a> to help you to train TensorFlow Lite models for embedded devices in the cloud.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-29T00:26:19.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"margaretmz/awesome-tensorflow-lite","categoryHTML":"<h2>Plugins and SDKs</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/am15h/tflite_flutter_plugin/\">TensorFlow Lite Flutter Plugin</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/am15h/tflite_flutter_plugin/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">361</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":361,\"repo\":\"am15h/tflite_flutter_plugin\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Provides a dart API similar to the TensorFlow Lite Java API for accessing TensorFlow Lite interpreter and performing inference in flutter apps. <a href=\"https://pub.dev/packages/tflite_flutter\">tflite_flutter on pub.dev</a>.</li>","updatedAt":"2020-09-29T00:26:19.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"margaretmz/awesome-tensorflow-lite","categoryHTML":"<h2>Helpful links</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sayakpaul/Adventures-in-TensorFlow-Lite\">Adventures in TensorFlow Lite</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sayakpaul/Adventures-in-TensorFlow-Lite\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\